---
import BaseLayout from "~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About usequickutils.com — a hyper-fast, privacy-first alternative to bloated legacy web utility sites.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-6">About QuickUtils</h1>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        QuickUtils was built with a singular goal: provide the fastest, most privacy-respecting 
        browser-based utility tools on the internet. We believe utility tools should be instant, 
        distraction-free, and completely private.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        Unlike other sites that clutter your screen with ads and upload your files to servers, 
        QuickUtils processes everything locally using HTML5 Canvas and JavaScript APIs. 
        Your files never leave your device.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">Why QuickUtils?</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc pl-5">
        <li><strong>100% Local Processing</strong> — Nothing is uploaded to any server</li>
        <li><strong>Zero Bloat</strong> — Clean, minimal interface with no unnecessary scripts</li>
        <li><strong>Lightning Fast</strong> — Static MPA architecture for instant page loads</li>
        <li><strong>Privacy First</strong> — No tracking, no data collection, no storage</li>
        <li><strong>Completely Free</strong> — No sign-ups, no paywalls, no limits</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">Technology</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        Built with Astro JS, Tailwind CSS, and the HTML5 Canvas API. Hosted as a static site 
        for maximum performance and reliability. Every page is a standalone HTML file for 
        optimal SEO and crawl efficiency.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
